* Happy birthday *

11:59.900 --> 12:02.700
* Dear Evy *
* Dear Grandma *

12:03.600 --> 12:08.900
* Happy birthday to you. *

12:09.000 --> 12:11.300
My boys, my boys.

12:11.400 --> 12:12.700
Thank you.

12:12.700 --> 12:13.600
Make a wish.

12:13.800 --> 12:16.000
Why? You're already here.

12:16.100 --> 12:17.400
My wish has come true.

12:21.500 --> 12:23.900
Who wishes for two gay guys
and a Chinese kid?

12:26.700 --> 12:30.400
Evy, now we have a very
special present for you.

12:31.300 --> 12:33.700
What do you think,
a bear eating a bear?

12:35.500 --> 12:38.000
Changpu is going to perform
a cello concerto.

12:38.100 --> 12:40.200
He wrote it himself,
in your honor.

12:40.300 --> 12:42.000
How marvelous.

12:46.000 --> 12:47.500
Should I give her
the card now?

12:47.800 --> 12:49.800
Forget about
the card, Jake.

12:50.200 --> 12:51.400
Shh, shh, shh.

12:51.500 --> 12:53.100
Shampoo is gonna play.

